<p data-start="230" data-end="281">For a portfolio project, I'd completely rewrite it.</p>
<p data-start="283" data-end="316">Here's the structure I would use:</p>
<div class="group relative clear-both my-4 w-full overflow-visible" data-writing-block-fullscreen-fallback-target="inline"><div id="writing-block-92cba927-ea18-4b19-9cda-9f1a311b501e" class="relative isolate w-full overflow-clip rounded-[24px] shadow-[0px_4px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)]" data-writing-block="true" data-testid="writing-block-container"><div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-1 rounded-[24px] bg-token-bg-primary dark:bg-[#2a2a2a]" data-writing-block-fullscreen-shell-surface="true"></div><div class="relative z-1"><div class="z-1 relative md:sticky md:top-(--sticky-padding-top)" data-testid="writing-block-header-sticky-container"><div class="relative isolate flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-3 font-sans py-2.5 pe-3" data-testid="writing-block-header-surface" style="padding-left: calc(1 * var(--spacing));"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-1 dark:bg-[#2a2a2a]" data-writing-block-fullscreen-header-surface="true"></div><div class="relative z-1 flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-3" data-writing-block-fullscreen-header-chrome="true" data-writing-block-fullscreen-header-layout="inline"><div class="flex grow gap-3 items-center"><div class="flex min-w-0 grow items-center self-start px-2"><div data-testid="writing-block-header-magic-edit-entrypoint" data-header-magic-edit-entrypoint-version="v1" class="z-2 relative flex min-w-0 items-center self-start shrink-0"><div data-testid="writing-block-header-magic-edit-leading-icon-slot" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 z-3 flex items-center" style="inset-inline-start: 0px;"><span class="flex size-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-[43px]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon shrink-0 text-token-text-primary"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></div><div data-testid="writing-bloc