<h2 data-start="1494" data-end="1530">Your final architecture should be</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1532" data-end="2194"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0a715c44.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>DATA LAYER</span><br><span>├── Synthetic Dataset Generation</span><br><span>├── Validation</span><br><span>└── Processing</span><br><br><span>↓</span><br><span>MODEL LAYER</span><br><span>├── Qwen Models</span><br><span>├── LoRA</span><br><span>├── PEFT</span><br><span>└── Quantization</span><br><br><span>↓</span><br><span>ALIGNMENT LAYER</span><br><span>├── Baseline</span><br><span>├── SFT</span><br><span>├── DPO</span><br><span>└── Checkpointing</span><br><br><span>↓</span><br><span>EVALUATION LAYER</span><br><span>├── Benchmarking</span><br><span>├── Hallucination Analysis</span><br><span>├── JSON Validation</span><br><span>└── Comparison</span><br><br><span>↓</span><br><span>RESEARCH LAYER</span><br><span>├── Attention Analysis</span><br><span>├── Gradient Analysis</span><br><span>├── Layer Drift</span><br><span>└── Forgetting Analysis</span><br><br><span>↓</span><br><span>SERVING LAYER</span><br><span>├── FastAPI</span><br><span>├── Inference Engine</span><br><span>├── Batching</span><br><span>└── Streaming</span><br><br><span>↓</span><br><span>MONITORING LAYER</span><br><span>├── GPU Metrics</span><br><span>├── Latency</span><br><span>├── Throughput</span><br><span>└── Resource Tracking</span><br><br><span>↓</span><br><span>DEPLOYMENT LAYER</span><br><span>├── Docker</span><br><span>├── Kubernetes</span><br><span>├── Model Registry</span><br><span>└── Autoscaling</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
